data.description: Welcome to the stunning 152 Ashley Bluffs. This beautiful home has all you could possibly need and more. You can sit on the front porch, enjoy coffee and the sounds of the gorgeous pond fountains directly across from the home.  Lovely hardwood floors throughout and carpet in the upstairs bedrooms. An office/flex room with doors is located on the main level with all 4 large bedrooms and loft upstairs. The home features high ceilings, board and batten walls, a gorgeous kitchen with ample counter/cabinet space, and a spacious open floor plan. The garage is the perfect spot for a man cave! If you're a nature lover, you're sure to fall in love with the backyard. Hot tub and outdoor kitchen to convey. This home is a must-see!
